parameters:
Upon being led into the building, I was quickly able to make
contact with the person who seemed to be the manager here.

Just as Akane said, she seems to have connections with this
person, and the conversation appeared to be going smoothly.

In hindsight, even if it was an introduction by a
trustworthy person, I should have been more skeptical about
how easily they allowed a complete stranger to gather
information inside the store...
